title: Did Julie Brickman lose her job after she got out of Trump, and then she was elected at the county house to the golf club?
subtitle: It is reported that one of the Trump golf clubs is located in the province where Julie Brickman now holds an elected seat.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: In January 2021, Julie Brickman, a Democrat from Virginia who once turned on the procession of President Donald Trump, was elected to a position in a jurisdiction where one of his golf clubs is located.
